{"tid":1193283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 最後召集","createTime":"2019-06-08T23:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T23:23:39.000Z","uid":40679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb99484f3cfaaac9c6201c843559c75cde15b7e","tid":1193283,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:22:33.000Z","msg":"我係英國人 亦都係香港人<br />\n我由細到大都係喺香港長大<br />\n好鍾意呢到嘅文化 呢到嘅所有野<br />\n但係呢幾年嘅變化真係令我好失望<br />\n更心痛嘅係 有一班所謂香港人連為自己爭取民主嘅鬥心都冇<br />\n俾人踩到上心口 都只係識講<br />\n關我咩事？ 是旦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 翻工啊！ <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n我 係香港人 就算我拎住英國公民passport <br />\n我都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n我都走出嚟為自己，為你地爭取嘅時候<br />\n點解你會覺得唔關你事？<br />\n<br />\n總撚知一句講哂<br />\n<br />\n不散 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjuDYtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjuDYtd.png&h=47c0df07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c36fd4b81dc7aa4a8babf2387e4d32f7848eaff","tid":1193283,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:23:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}